Index external packages (stdlib, site-packages) into global cache

Usage: normalize index packages [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --only <ONLY>  Ecosystems to index (python, go, js, deno, java, cpp, rust). Defaults to all available
      --clear        Clear existing index before re-indexing
  -r, --root <ROOT>  Root directory (defaults to current directory)
      --json         Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>    Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty       Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact      Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help         Print help
